Class State

    Logable, StateInterface, Serializable

    public class State
extends FunctionState
    This is a facade for the various stateful components we have to track. Represents the internal state of the system. It has the ImportManager, SymbolTable, MetaEvaluator and such.

    Created by Jeff Gaynor
    on 1/21/20 at 7:25 AM
